Package tiger.utils

Class CustomDate

  • java.lang.Object
    • tiger.utils.CustomDate
  • public class CustomDate
extends java.lang.Object
    The CustomDate class represents possible input dates that the user wishes to key in. A date, localDate, is necessary, however a localTime may not be necessary, in the case for all day tasks. This is indicated by a boolean variable hasTime.
